-- Audi Saradar Investment Bank Sets Up MENA Equity Sales Team
-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 2012-02-20T11:35:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/audi-saradar-investment-bank-sets-up-mena-equity-sales-team.html
Audi Saradar Investment Bank SAL, a
branch of Audi Saradar Group based in  Beirut , Lebanon, set up a
 Middle East  and North Africa equity sales team, newly appointed
head of sales Mahdi Mattar said.  Mattar will help build the division, which will also cover
 Turkey , he said by phone from Beirut today. Mattar joined the
bank last week after leaving Abu Dhabi-based CAPM Investment
PJSC, where he was head of research.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
 zhankir@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  